Package: statConsultantAddin
Type: Package
Title: Stat Consultant RStudio Addin
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Hideyuki", "Wanaka", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "ceh.2o4l.amrmtsc@gmail.com")
Description: RStudio Addin for Stat Consultant. Starts the bundled backend,
    opens the chat UI, then polls the backend's pending-code queue and inserts
    received code at the cursor position of the active source document
    (rstudioapi::insertText). Also transparently scans the global environment
    and syncs an aggregate-only, PII-filtered snapshot (column names/types/
    missing counts/category levels — never row values) to the backend.
    Zero-config auth via a local shared-secret file the backend generates.
License: Proprietary
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
